title: Valar Rereadis: TWOIAF - The Rage of Heroes
description:
A look at how the different regions view their various founding figures, and the patterns and comparisons within. Especially Garth Greenhand, Lann the Clever, the Grey King and Durran Godsgrief, but also houses with stories that don't center on a person, like House Dayne or House Dondarrion.
